title: The Start Here Tour (Friday)
short_description: Start your Art Institute visit with a one-stop tour led by a knowledgeable guide. Get a peek at the collection, learn about the day’s events, and receive tips for navigating the museum. All are welcome—whether this is your first time at the Art Institute or your one hundred and first.
